    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "> How does it behave when combined with routing on initial load with a state in the url?\r\n\r\nNothing is implemented right now since routing is not updated (yet). For a first version I think an override (or shallow merge) will be enough otherwise we have to implement a merge function for `UiState`. This is something that I would like to avoid as much as possible. Another alternative is to allow the user to provide its own function to perform the merge. ",
